											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The player stops, confused, as Yenna comes running towards them out of the undercity shadows. She is bloodied and bruised, limping as though she'd been seriously hurt, shouting back into the darkness. In the distance, we hear a woman giggling. (Orin - emote recorded within Nested dialogue). It's terrifying."
												}
