			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "To trigger the In-World Abductions\r\n1) \nCTRL+SHIFT+9 (Debug book) Go to Region -> Act 3 -> Undercity -> Bhaal Temple -> In-World Abdcution 1.\n\r\n2) CTRL+SHIFT+8 (Camp debug book) - Invite Individual -> Yenna\n\r\n3) Walk forward a bit down the stairs and you should trigger the event. Orin-as-Yenna will run towards you and start the dialog.\r\n4) If you want to try the other abduction location, you'll need to reload and use debug book to go to the other 3 locations."
				},
